    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The function likely checks the input date against predefined fiscal year boundaries. For example, if a fiscal year starts on July 1st and ends on June 30th of the following year, the function would determine if the input date falls within such a range. The logic involves:"
        }
